{"tid":1593483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】【10.1】【主線】【SUCK泥馬】【國慶】【賀佢老母】【SUCK小隊】SUCK 特備節目","createTime":"2019-09-25T05:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:22:47.000Z","uid":282534,"like":75,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"0c30390320387a0c06a9d4160d6e5abf945001e5","tid":1593483,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong></strong></span></span>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRecASK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXRecASK.png&h=6230cfe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WpWKrZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpWKrZC.jpg&h=a2d4df6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國慶</span></span>喎！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中華人哋共和國中央人叫政府成立70週年喎！</span></span><br />\n咁重要嘅日子我哋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">SUCK</span></span>又點可以唔<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span></span>呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國慶賀佢老母</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一國兩制 馬照跑 舞照跳<br />\n一國一制 馬不跑 舞不跳</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地一齊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">SUCK爆馬場觀眾席</span></span>!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nadmin好想見到大家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">玩馬場人海</span></span>!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"></span></span></strong> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">國慶杯</span></span>想同大家一齊入沙田馬場 齊齊唱<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></strong></span>!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n我都知大家未入過馬場睇馬仔.. <br />\n俾一次機會大家入去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"></span></strong></span>!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n同時亦歡迎各界<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>記者朋友</strong></span></span>到場影相~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n詳細解說點解要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">玩馬場</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先國慶杯係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際賽事</span></span>,<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong></strong></span></span><br />\n而且<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">12點會有唱國歌儀式</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唱歌就點少得榮光呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一日派發獎金連同投注額隨時可以有幾億上落.</span></span><br />\n而且係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國慶杯</span></span>,<br />\n一定有勁多<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>國內,香港,外國高官貴人</strong></span></span>,<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有任何畫面即刻<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>國際頭版</strong></span></span>.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n打<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong></strong></span></span>必定係首選.<br />\n往年既國慶杯活動都會由<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特首 高官</span></span>之類既人物去派獎,<br />\n今年會點冇人知<br />\n另外不斷有人話會分散人手<br />\n其實<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國慶杯就兩場賽事</span></span>,完左做完畫面可以即刻<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">出番港島遊行完全冇沖突</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信香港人既行動力 SUCK  4.0 亦證實左<br />\n另外去開維園遊行既人都知架啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">無四點你點行得郁</span></span>,如期係維園等,不如係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">等既呢段時間做一次有效既打擊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">馬迷 we connect</span></span> , <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔會搞到佢無馬跑 .但我地要上晒國際頭版.</span></span><br />\n&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">膠既打氣大聲公</span></span>一定係首選.<br />\n&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且最最最重要,係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國一定冇晒臉</span></span>.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n期待各位影帝表演<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFFy7nV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFFy7nV.jpg&h=a778d420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n附上攻略<br />\n<br />\n<strong>沙田馬場平時將於<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11點開放入場</span></span><br />\n由於國慶杯係大型賽事<br />\n10點半就好多人排隊<br />\n好快<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">終點線就爆滿</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11點要入場霸靚位啦!!!!<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記者朋友</span></span>你地成日望住我地架啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記得去馬場呀 </span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要去既記得早早排隊霸位<br />\n馬場好早好快就滿坐架啦</span></span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\ndress code : 自己換衫 唔提 唔提 同大球場一樣<br />\n道具 : 大型banner , jbi/sony speaker 可以connect party mode , 膠既大聲公 等<br />\n入場費 : 於10月1日國慶賽馬日可免費進入沙田馬場公眾席<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioPspLX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioPspLX.jpg&h=4d2138dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後係呢度 admin有野想講<br />\n<br />\n經過 admin 團 一眾考慮<br />\n決定和你suck 和你塞<br />\n呢個名俾大家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隨意使用 遍地開花</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家可以一直將數字延續落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本channel 同SUCK 往後行動將只會使用  <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">SUCK  加 當次活動代號code <br />\n同 最新文宣logo 以作識別之用</span></span><br />\n例 : SUCK 狼來了 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同場宣佈 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">原機場行動和你塞admin</span></span> 將正式改名為<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">【SUCK小隊】</span></span>  以方便識別<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">【SUCK小隊】<br />\n</span></span>想<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">俾各種和你塞行動遍地開花</span></span> <br />\n大家加油  齊塞齊上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10.1 兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n<br />\n10.1 SUCK 泥馬 (沙田馬場)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10.1 和你suck 5.0 機場(連登自發)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592471</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSUCK channel - <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9D11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=71f35c8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\nSUCK 公海 - <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9D11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=d86037e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a>"},{"pid":"dd896549f7ffa555604c7e2cbc107e70631199d6","tid":1593483,"uid":47605,